Nightmare Mudlib 3.2 SimulEfun: tell_room()

varargs void tell_room(object, string|int, object|object *);

DESCRIPTION
Tells to all objects in the inventory of the first argument the message
represented by the second argument.  An optional third argument allows
you to exclude and object or array of objects from receiving message.

LOCATION
/adm/simul_efun/communications.c

SEE ALSO
message(), say(), shout(), tell_object(), write()
